id: pmc-f4yg
title: Expose item-url-base through pm changelog extension command
description: "GitHub #7: package CLI and generator support itemUrlBase, but the pm extension command rejects --item-url-base and cannot generate clickable pm item references through the default pm package flow."
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 0
tags[4]: changelog,extension,links,release
