comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T12:46:30.453Z",codex-pm-changelog-fix,"Evidence: GitHub issue unbraind/pm-changelog#7 filed and corrected. Fix exposes --item-url-base in src/extension.ts and passes itemUrlBase into createChangelog/writeChangelog. npm run release:check passed in repo context; PM_PATH sandbox override was intentionally not used for that gate because changelog:check must read the package repository pm history."
